Right?
Different sets of instructions.

00:36:45.949 --> 00:36:47.879
Anything else strike you as odd
when you were reading this

00:36:47.879 --> 00:36:48.150
story?
 

00:36:48.150 --> 00:36:51.289
 
 

00:36:51.289 --> 00:36:53.493
Student: [inaudible]
Professor Christine

00:36:53.493 --> 00:36:55.381
Hayes: Okay,
rain seems to be there for

00:36:55.381 --> 00:36:57.269
different amounts of time,
