00:37:17.950 --> 00:37:23.460
 
 

00:37:23.460 --> 00:37:24.030
Who's giving the instructions?
 

00:37:24.030 --> 00:37:28.780
 
 

00:37:28.780 --> 00:37:30.958
That's not hard;
you have it right in front of

00:37:30.958 --> 00:37:32.519
you.
Who's giving the instructions?

